@database aghelp.guide

@node Main "Assistant main help screen"

                    Welcome to Assistant.


Assistant is a program that can help you to remember appointments, keep
your todo lists organized, remember your addresses and convert between
different units.


  @{"Copyright   " link COPR} - Copyright & Credits.

  @{"Gadgets     " link GADG} - Gadgets on the main screen.

  @{"Menus       " link MENU} - Menus on the main screen.

  @{"Panels      " link PANE} - The controle panels.

  @{"History     " link HIST} - A look at the past.

  @{"Future      " link FUTU} - A look at the future.


I hope that you enjoy the program.
@endnode



